data.text:
Description

Founder, chairman, and CEO of Dell Technologies (born 1965) which has grown into one of the world's largest technology infrastructure companies. Dell Computer business card belonging to Michael Dell, 3.5 x 2, which identifies him as "Chairman of the Board, Chief Executive Officer," signed in black ink, "M. Dell." In very fine condition, with a JSA label affixed to the reverse. Encapsulated by Beckett Authentication Services.
